Distribution. Maldives , Sri Lanka , Bay of Bengal, Indonesia , northern Australia , Philippines , China (A. M. Clark and Rowe 1971 ); Myanmar (A. M. Clark 1972 ); southern Vietnam ( Mekhova and Britayev 2012 ); Papua New Guinea , Micronesia ( Meyer and Macurda 1980 ; Messing 1994 ); Timor Sea ( Rowe and Gates 1995 ); South Pacific Ocean (A. M. Clark and Rowe 1971 ); South China Sea (
Lane et al. 2000
); Taiwan (
Chen et al. 1988
); Japan (A. M. Clark and Rowe 1971 ; Kogo 1998 , 2006 ; Pilcher and Messing 2001 ; Kogo and Fujita 2005 ). Depth range: 0–210 m (
Lane et al. 2000
).
